Dad!

20:07.506 --> 20:09.441
All right,
what the hell is going on?

20:09.741 --> 20:11.810
No idea. I just came by
for my paycheck.

20:11.810 --> 20:12.778
MARTIN:
Well, uh..

20:13.178 --> 20:14.246
I got some bad news about that, Trish.

20:14.746 --> 20:16.582
I'm sorry, but we're going to have to let you go.

20:16.848 --> 20:18.417
Oh. Okay.
But you still owe me

20:18.417 --> 20:20.752
for the days I was supposed
to be here last week.

20:21.053 --> 20:23.589
Sure, sure, and there'll be
a check in the mail

20:24.089 --> 20:26.592
sometime after the first..

20:27.125 --> 20:29.428
asteroid hits Earth.

20:34.733 --> 20:36.235
Okay, lay it on me

20:36.235 --> 20:38.237
I'm-I'm prepared for the worst.

20:38.237 --> 20:40.038
Is it my heart?

20:40.239 --> 20:41.306
I'm afraid so.

20:41.740 --> 20:43.308
Aha!

20:44.810 --> 20:46.778
What?

20:47.179 --> 20:48.247
There is an anomaly in your EKG.

20:48.747 --> 20:50.182
I'm going to have
to check you into

20:50.582 --> 20:52.150
the hospital.

20:52.150 --> 20:53.652
Oh. Uh, well, hm.

20:54.152 --> 20:55.654
Uh, I guess I can clear
my schedule.

20:56.154 --> 20:57.656
Uh, how's, uh,
how's tomorrow afternoon?

20:58.123 --> 20:59.925
No, no, no. Niles?
Hm?

21:00.125 --> 21:01.693
You need to go right now.

